member.name: T:Ict.Petra.Client.MPartner.TPartnerEditDSWinForm
member.summary: More summary details go here. (-->comes from external XML file)
member.remarks:
Features:
the top part of the screen is collapsible (useful with 800x600 resolution)
the lower part uses large exchangable TabControls with many TabPages to incorporate many Petra 4GL screens on different tabs
several sections of the screen resize when the form is resized
populating the screen with data is done with just one call to the UIConnector and all data is returned as a result of this method call - very low amount of data transfer is archieved through this!
all data of all (populated) fields on the screen is held in only one Typed DataSet, which holds several Typed DataTables. All (populated) fields are DataBound to fields in DataTables in this DataSet
saving data is also very easy: just submit the changed/new/deleted Rows to the UIConnector class and see if errors are returned
1..n Addresses are displayed in a list control
Note: Replacement for 4GL Screen ma1000e.w (and many other 4GL screens that are now UserControls who are hosted on tabs!)
(-->All Remarks come from external XML file)
